	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p>p Plantajenet <date>5<hi rend="sup">th</hi> Sep.</date></p>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Kingston Jamaica</placeName></p>
				<p rend="align(right)"><date>4<hi rend="sup">th</hi> September 1863</date></p>
				<p><addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Dear Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">The <persName>Revd. Dr. M. N. Nathan</persName> has handed<lb/> me for Sale on your a&#47;c the following&#58;</p>
				<table rows="7" cols="2">
				<row>
				<cell>&#40;3&#41; Three Quarto Bibles &#64;</cell>
				<cell>&#36;6.00</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>&#40;3&#41; Three do do &#64;</cell>
				<cell>&#36;8.&#8212;</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>&#40;2&#41; Two Daily Prayers &#64;</cell>
				<cell>&#36;3.&#8212;</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>&#40;1&#41; One do do</cell>
				<cell>&#36;3&#8212;</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>&#40;3&#41; Three sets Pentateuch &#38; <date>Sabbath</date> Prayers &#64;</cell>
				<cell>&#36;7&#8212;</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>&#40;20&#41; Twenty Catechisms for Jewish Children &#64;</cell>
				<cell>2&#47;6 ea</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>&#40;2&#41; Two requisition &#38; Judaism</cell>
				<cell/>
				</row>
				</table>
				<p>and a lot Old numbers of the Occident</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">The Revd Dr. has given me the above as the<lb/> selling prices from which my commissions as Agent<lb/> are to be deducted.  You will please inform me<lb/> what commission you allow or perhaps you will<lb/> consign your books at the lowest selling price&#44; deducting<lb/> all discounts&#44; and leave me to make my commissions<lb/> and expenses from the profit I may make on sales<lb/> effected.  Remittances to be made whenever the amt<lb/> of sales is large enough and to cover invoice cost.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I require by return steamer to leave <placeName>New York</placeName><lb/> about the <date>20<hi rend="sup">th</hi></date> or <date>21<hi rend="sup">st</hi></date> inst one set Hebrew &#38; English<lb/> Prayer Books for Spanish &#38; Portuguese Synagogue</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p>without Pentateuch or Prophets to sell here at from &#163;4 to<lb/> &#163;5.  It would be well for you to consign a few sets<lb/> but if you do not do so by the return mail I trust<lb/> you will not disappoint me by not forwarding the<lb/> one set.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Parcels sent to <placeName>New York</placeName> prepaid to <persName>Henry<lb/> de Cordova &#38; Co.</persName> will be duly forwarded</p>
			<p rend="indent(11)">Yours very truly</p>
			<p rend="indent(11)"><persName role="author">M de Cordova</persName></p>
			<pb n="3"/>
				<p><addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
		</body>
	</text>
